      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 13:30:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普 8 万亿美元的涨势将受到艰难财报季的考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/s-p-s-8-trillion-rally-will-be-tested-by-tricky-earnings-season</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年股市开局火爆，交易员们正面临一系列风险，从经济恐慌到利率不确定性，再到选举焦虑。但或许，决定股市能否继续上涨的最重要变量本周再次成为人们关注的焦点：企业盈利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/s-p-s-8-trillion-rally-will-be-tested-by-tricky-earnings-season</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 13:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
